<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IAS24_28B"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>28B</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS&#xa0;24"/><data name="paranum" value="28B"/></prolog><body><variant base="F21341298" id="IAS24_28B_V1"> <p id="IAS24_P0177"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> (Amendments to <xref base="F24730932" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_TOC.dita#IFRS10_TOC0001" id="IAS24_X0151">IFRS&#xa0;10</xref>, <xref base="F24730933" href="../ifrs12/IFRS12_TOC.dita#IFRS12_TOC0001" id="IAS24_X0152">IFRS&#xa0;12</xref> and <xref base="F24730934" href="../ias27/IAS27_TOC0001.dita#IAS27_TOC0001" id="IAS24_X0153">IAS&#xa0;27</xref>), issued in October 2012, amended <xref base="F24730935" href="IAS24_4.dita#IAS24_4/IAS24_4_V2" id="IAS24_X0154">paragraphs 4</xref> and <xref base="F24730936" href="IAS24_9.dita#IAS24_9" id="IAS24_X0155">9</xref>. An entity shall apply those amendments for annual periods beginning on or after 1 January 2014. Earlier application of <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> is permitted. If an entity applies those amendments earlier it shall also apply all amendments included in <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> at the same time.</p></variant></body></paragraph>